chat.default-title.description: The title of the chat window

chat.allow.message: Allow AI chatbot to answer questions

The accuracy, completeness, or timeliness of the information provided is not guaranteed, and we do not assume any responsibility or liability for the use or interpretation of this content.

chatbot.feedback.dialog.send.description: This is part of a feedback dialog box. The user clicks this button to send their comment.
